class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site features a trendy design that highlights the artist's Native American style through background colors, dripping paint, and the logo. There is a lot of information on the site, dotted around in text blocks, which creates a busy look but offers all the information that the viewer could possibly want.</p><p>A combination of photos, links, and videos creates visual interest. While the gallery is not very extensive, visitors can click on the images to see more information, different-sized images, and the story behind the image.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
