</span>
<span>Albany, New York, U.S.</span></p><div
class="entry-text"><p>This simple website acts as the online portfolio for this abstract artist, including a bio, examples of his work, and a resume. The design of the site echoes the artist's work, which acts as a good marketing tool and places all emphasis on the work itself.</p><p>Visitors to the site are able to read the artist's bio, statement, and resume, but while there is a shopping cart symbol in the menu, the page is not available, and users cannot purchase paintings online. The site would also benefit from customer reviews and a newsletter.</p></div><h4>Pros and Cons</h4><div
class="entry-indented-box"><div
class="entry-website-pros">
