class="entry-text"><p>The desktop site has a simple, yet sometimes non-intuitive design structure, featuring only three pages that highlight the artist's work, bio, resume, and contact information. Some of the images can be enlarged, while some can't, and some images have the option to contact the artist for pricing.</p><p>The contact page features a simple message box, while the third page, headed by a shopping cart, features an empty page as there is actually no way to buy the pieces online. The background of the site mimics the artist's abstract style, focusing all attention on the work itself.</p></div></div><h4>Mobile Review</h4><div
