class="entry-text"><p>The mobile site welcomes viewers with the artist's name front and center and an example of his artwork, perfectly sized to the smaller screen. The text blocks, however, look as if they're cut off because they are oriented to the right and left margins, respectively.</p><p>The images of the artist's work look good on the screen, but clicking on the image to enlarge it does not make as much impact as on the desktop. The mobile site leaves out the empty cart page included on the desktop and has a 61/100 performance rating on Google's PageSpeed Insights report.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div
